codex
The first configured run exposed an important initialization issue: a denied filter starts at ECEF zero, where Doppler geometry is undefined. I’m making the receiver prior explicit in the replay configuration (not derived from truth or GNSS journals) and excluding prior seeding from the journal measurement-update count. This keeps denied authority semantics intact and makes the synthetic comparison honest about its starting condition.
